---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout>
  <Fragment slot="head">
    <title>Testimonials | LEM Building Surveying Ltd</title>
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="Read reviews from homeowners and landlords who have used LEM Building Surveying Ltd for RICS surveys, damp reports and property assessments."
    />
  </Fragment>

  <main class="box-container">
    <section class="testimonial-section">
      <h1>Client Testimonials</h1>
      <p>
        From first-time buyers to portfolio landlords, our clients value clear reporting,
        honest advice and quick turnaround times. The live widget below pulls in our latest
        Google and direct reviews. A few highlights are included for easy reference.
      </p>

      <article class="testimonial-highlight">
        <h2>What Clients Say</h2>
        <p>
          “Liam explained everything in plain English and spotted issues we never would have
          seen ourselves. The report arrived ahead of schedule and helped us negotiate money
          off the purchase price.” – Residential buyer, Chester
        </p>
        <p>
          “We needed an urgent damp assessment for a rental property. LEM Building Surveying
          provided a thorough inspection and a practical action plan we could share with our
          contractor.” – Landlord, Flintshire
        </p>
        <p>
          “Measured survey drawings were delivered quickly and accurately, allowing our
          architect to progress planning designs without delay.” – Homeowner, Tarvin
        </p>
      </article>

      <p>
        We encourage every client to share feedback to ensure our service keeps improving.
        You can read more reviews or add your own through the widget below.
      </p>

      <div class="ti-widget ti-goog"></div>
      <script
        src="https://cdn.trustindex.io/loader.js?f82e0f551228447e6c06f9b86c7"
        async
        defer
        is:inline
      ></script>

      <div class="cta-section">
        <a class="cta-button" href="/enquiry.html">Request a Survey Quote</a>
        <a class="secondary-button" href="/contact.html">Share Your Experience</a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
